deleteSimple

public void deleteSimple(int i)
Deletes keys [i] and ptrs [i] from this node, without performing any combination or redistribution afterwards. Does so by shifting all keys and pointers from index i+1 on one position to the left. Differs from LeafNode routine in that updates parent references of all ptrs from index i+1 on.

Specified by:
deleteSimple in class Node
Parameters:
i - the index of the key to delete
